1141
00:33:26,950 --> 00:33:28,560
(Trendy?)

1142
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:30,470
Let me play a tune on the erhu
for everyone.

1143
00:33:30,470 --> 00:33:32,220
(Something down-to-earth)

1144
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:33,520
This one looks good.

1145
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:34,800
(Want it)
Can I try yours on?

1146
00:33:35,310 --> 00:33:36,560
He'd look great wearing that.

1147
00:33:37,230 --> 00:33:37,950
I'm sure.

1148
00:33:37,950 --> 00:33:38,920
I'm really looking forward to it.

1149
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:40,760
I really like yours.

1150
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,190
It matches perfectly.

1151
00:33:43,190 --> 00:33:43,800
Looks great.

1152
00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:44,430
(Everyone agrees.)
Really looks great.

1153
00:33:44,430 --> 00:33:45,160
It actually suits him quite well.

1154
00:33:45,430 --> 00:33:46,110
This one's really nice.

1155
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,830
(Taking another good look)

1156
00:33:47,830 --> 00:33:49,190
You've got delicate features.

1157
00:33:49,190 --> 00:33:50,230
So this gold-rimmed style...

1158
00:33:50,230 --> 00:33:51,110
Wait, is it tilted a bit?

1159
00:33:51,110 --> 00:33:51,950
Yeah, it's a bit tilted.

1160
00:33:57,710 --> 00:33:59,040
What are you doing?

1161
00:33:59,040 --> 00:34:00,230
I'm about to eat my egg.

1162
00:34:00,230 --> 00:34:00,920
I want some too.

1163
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:02,430
Okay, you can have one bite.

1164
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:06,430
It's all stretchy.

1165
00:34:06,430 --> 00:34:06,950
I don't want that stringy bit.

1166
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:08,080
Then open your mouth.

1167
00:34:15,390 --> 00:34:16,470
Think you can win today?

1168
00:34:17,080 --> 00:34:17,670
I'll do my best.

1169
00:34:19,150 --> 00:34:20,320
You've got to give it your all too.

1170
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:20,630
Alright.

1171
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:23,230
I will.

1172
00:34:25,980 --> 00:34:42,940
("Live and Love" S2 Release Schedule)

1173
00:34:43,190 --> 00:34:43,950
So happy.

1174
00:34:43,950 --> 00:34:46,060
(Watch Live and Love with us)
Back again for more romance!

1175
00:34:46,470 --> 00:34:48,510
(on Thu. 12 PM.)
The two guys are fighting.

1176
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:49,550
They're shaking it again.

1177
00:34:50,790 --> 00:34:51,550
I just love

1178
00:34:51,550 --> 00:34:52,100
this subtle vibe

1179
00:34:52,100 --> 00:34:53,990
in the air.

1180
00:34:53,990 --> 00:34:55,430
I want them all messed up.

1181
00:34:55,690 --> 00:34:56,790
(Interesting)

1182
00:34:56,790 --> 00:34:58,060
Make her choose between two men.

1183
00:34:58,060 --> 00:34:59,340
Seeing Lu Yanting right now,

1184
00:34:59,340 --> 00:34:59,990
I just can't help laughing.

1185
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:01,950
Why is he

1186
00:35:01,950 --> 00:35:02,860
messing with others?

1187
00:35:03,060 --> 00:35:05,380
Zhang Zizheng just froze.

1188
00:35:05,660 --> 00:35:06,550
She's kind of like...

1189
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:08,430
Afraid she'll get eliminated.

1190
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,660
What's going on?

1191
00:35:13,580 --> 00:35:15,140
(Balance Island Special Event on Friday PM.)
Attention, islanders.

1192
00:35:15,140 --> 00:35:18,010
(Love Flight Chess)
Today we'll play two rounds.

1193
00:35:19,060 --> 00:35:19,950
It's a guaranteed win.

1194
00:35:19,950 --> 00:35:21,060
(Excited)
Six!

1195
00:35:21,130 --> 00:35:21,890
(Luck skipped me this time.)

1196
00:35:22,270 --> 00:35:23,470
(Failed to take off in the second round)
Almost got a six.

1197
00:35:23,470 --> 00:35:24,100
I'm so mad right now.

1198
00:35:24,140 --> 00:35:25,860
These two are about to throw down.

1199
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:26,550
No way.

1200
00:35:26,550 --> 00:35:27,710
(Stops)
I didn't throw just now.

1201
00:35:27,790 --> 00:35:29,620
What made you cry last time?

1202
00:35:29,620 --> 00:35:32,190
Name your partner's habit
you can't stand.

1203
00:35:32,190 --> 00:35:33,950
Who on the island
are you jealous of?

1204
00:35:33,990 --> 00:35:35,230
I actually know quite a bit.

1205
00:35:35,340 --> 00:35:36,820
And then I just started crying.

1206
00:35:36,860 --> 00:35:38,230
I just can't escape your hold.

1207
00:35:38,970 --> 00:35:39,530
(Really corny)

1208
00:35:39,620 --> 00:35:40,750
I will win.

1209
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:42,710
That's hilarious.
